snippet.title: Monster Hunter Wilds The Hunter's Journey Official Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2024
snippet.description: Prepare to experience the most cinematic and immersive story in Monster Hunter series history. Find out what lies in store for you and your allies in this vast, seamless land teeming with monsters, when Monster Hunter Wilds launches on PS5 in 2025.
